      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in museum-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Mechanically flawless, the double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and rod bearing shells were replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains rigid with a documented subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile shifts, paired with a perfectly calibrated variable M differential lock. Finished in pristine factory paint with zero oxidation, this unit retains its original suspension kinematics and bushing integrity, providing the quintessential analog driving experience.",
